# alexhouston/w00t notation example.
# Source: https://boardgamegeek.com/thread/1764731/homeworlds-game-notation
# Player 1 is alexhouston. Player 2 is w00t.
# System IDs:
# 0 alexhouston, 1 w00t, 2 post, 3 boop, 4 bop.

# 1: homeworld setup
ym bl
gl
gl bs
yl

# 2
b 0 gs
b 1 ys

# 3
b 0 gs
b 1 ys

# 4
t 0 gs n bs
x 1 ys rs

# 5
x 0 gs ys
t 1 ys n gm

# 6
b 2 gs
b 1 rs

# 7
x 2 gs rs
t 1 rs x 3

# 8
b 2 rm
b 3 rm

# 9
b 2 gs
t 3 rm n gl

# 10
t 0 ys x 2
x 1 rs bs

show
